      "content": "it's not even just being sad. it's just... so exhausting. everything feels like so much work for nothing. i look at tomorrow and i just see more of this same emptiness. it's like there's no version of life where this weight ever actually goes away. it just feels like i'm carrying it for no reason anymore.",
